'''''Kampfgruppe''''' is a [[computer wargame]] designed by [[Gary Grigsby]] and published in 1984 by [[Strategic Simulations]] for the [[Apple II]], [[Atari 8-bit computers]], and [[Commodore 64]]. ''Kampfgruppe'' is a game of tactical-scale combat on the [[Eastern Front (World War II)|Eastern Front]].<ref name=cgw150/> An [[MS-DOS]] port was released in 1987 followed by an [[Amiga]] version in 1988.

